{"id":"8538f030-fc43-4af7-a27c-587b7a5cde2a","name":"MHA- Reaction Room","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Welcome to the Reaction Room with MHA!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">(let's try to make this work)</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">But I tried..</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/92253c61-93de-4f6a-abd9-43b329a67d36_0bf707c4-d9fb-4429-aafa-22e1dadb5002.webp?width=1000\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 305px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">I added Aizawa, Class 1-A, and the League of Villains. you control the videos so the characters can react. FYI you’re going to be the most powerful mystical being who’s just bored and doing this for fun. But you can choose if you're good or evil… you don't even have to change anything bout your persona this mythical stuff is just an addon where you can control everything. But to make this interesting no quirks works in this reaction room but only yours cause its your domain.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Goodluck…</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/92253c61-93de-4f6a-abd9-43b329a67d36_50904493-7467-4301-8859-efe0f4fe1447.webp?width=1000\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 305px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">TO FIND ME:</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Discord ┈➤<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FF4W6qxrjQG\" target=\"_blank\"> </a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"/exte